    "Management": {
      "text": "Surgical decompression\nAntibiotics\nVancomycin\n+\nmetronidazole\n+ (\ncefotaxime\nor\nceftriaxone\nor\nceftazidime\n)\nCeftazidime\nis preferred if\npseudomonas\nis considered likely\nCan substitute\nnafcillin\nor\noxacillin\nfor\nVancomycin\nif not\nMRSA\nTreat for 6-8 weeks\nIf likely nasopharyngeal source (\nsinusitis\n,\nmastoiditis\n), may consider regiment covering\nstrep\n,\nHaemophilus influenzae\n, and\naerobes",
